  "claim_short": "If an isometrically homogeneous space has arbitrarily almost-Hilbertian infinite-dimensional restrictions, then it is isometric to ell_2. More intrinsically, if the infimum of d(Y, ell_2) over closed infinite-dimensional subspaces Y is 1, then the space is isometric to ell_2.",
